{"tid":1471834,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【冷靜呀】即使敵人係惡魔，為民意我地千奇唔好打狗同埋蝗蟲呀！！！","createTime":"2019-08-14T11:25:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T16:02:16.000Z","uid":35699,"like":36,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6c5b4f43e35f86f32a39a9212b5ce980cc8a0adb","tid":1471834,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:25:54.000Z","msg":"【1900】有已核實身分的醫護人員聯絡本頻道，提供兩張荃灣被斬示威者（圖）送院時傷勢的照片。<br />\n<br />\n該名醫護呼籲，希望市民認清什麼才是真正的暴力，又稱不會指責昨晚在機場集會動手的示威者，因為兩個月以來不少示威者都被警察或者黑社會攻擊致受傷，而傷勢之重，與昨日於機場被打的疑似公安及環時記者根本無從比較，「好多人已經為呢件事付出好多，現在唔係指責或者割席嘅時候」。<br />\n<br />\n以下為傷勢照片，或會引起嚴重不安，查看前請務必做好心理準備。<br />\n<br />\n左腳傷勢：<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/z0k1UL0.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz0k1UL0.jpg&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3fno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=851328df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/z0k1UL0.jpg</a><br />\n右手傷勢：<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/oeH3751.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoeH3751.jpg&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3fno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=cd836ec3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/oeH3751.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">即使敵人係惡魔，為民意我地千奇唔好打狗同埋蝗蟲呀！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反對！為下一代一定要奮戰到底，狗狗底線有幾低，我地底線就有幾低！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同意！即使有人犧牲都唔會還手"},{"pid":"55c2206e27a3f0283604d2385e1a6472b3703aa3","tid":1471834,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:26:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"edb44a920534afb030319bee1a732bb6373a3df0","tid":1471834,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:27:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wS0PDYcWh8U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwS0PDYcWh8U&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3fno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=bd71e456\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wS0PDYcWh8U</a>"},{"pid":"5b692eb7cade3e6096629efcd268c13018e548b5","tid":1471834,"uid":35699,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"edb44a920534afb030319bee1a732bb6373a3df0","tid":1471834,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:27:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wS0PDYcWh8U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwS0PDYcWh8U&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3fno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=bd71e456\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wS0PDYcWh8U</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:28:34.000Z","msg":"1）近日hit and run 極之成功<br />\n點解突然間要退場？<br />\n已經很聰明地沒硬踫<br />\n<br />\n2）矛同盾<br />\n應該共同存在<br />\n只有矛 或 只有盾 都係唔可行"},{"pid":"cf521c1f030acc52d27052766459cd9a485ced3f","tid":1471834,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:28:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg&h=42f5c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540